<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="it">

<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <meta name="color-scheme" content="light only">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@4.3.1/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css"
    integrity="sha384-ggOyR0iXCbMQv3Xipma34MD+dH/1fQ784/j6cY/iJTQUOhcWr7x9JvoRxT2MZw1T" crossorigin="anonymous">
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Poppins:wght@300;500&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
</head>

<body style="font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif;">
  <div class="d-flex align-items-center container-fluid" style="height: 100vh; background-color: rgb(246, 246, 246); min-width: 400px;">
    <div class="w-50 my-auto container" style="min-width: 400px;">
      <div class="card my-3">
        <div class="py-3 text-center card-header"
          style="background: linear-gradient(rgb(42, 124, 228), rgb(33, 75, 126)); color: white; font-size: 25px; font-weight: bold;">
          Benvenuto in <span class="text-warning">P</span>Manager
        </div>
        <div class="card-body">
          <div class="py-2 card-title h5">
            Gentile {{nome}},
          </div>
          <p class="card-text">
            le comunichiamo la password temporanea con cui accedere alla sua nuova console.
          </p>
          <p class="py-3 text-center card-text">
            <span class="badge badge-secondary p-2" style="font-size: 20px; font-weight: bold;">
              {{password}}
            </span>
          </p>
          <p class="card-text">
            Al primo accesso le verrà richiesto di inserire una nuova password di cui solamente lei ne sarà a
            conoscenza.
          </p>
          <p class="p-3 card-text" style="font-weight: lighter; text-align: right;">Il team di PManager</p>
        </div>
        <div class="py-3 text-center card-footer">
          <button type="button" class="p-2 btn btn-warning" style="color: white; font-weight: bold;">
            Vai alla console
          </button>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>

</html>